{"2937940": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "無人島社員旅行記　～雌性間的生存戰爭～", "steam_appid": 2937940, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras/d9fb2ec2a5c691a43d3a2a6853e13126.avif?t=1761909441\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆遊戲背景概要◆</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一趟員工旅遊中，你與同事們搭乘的郵輪不幸沉沒，最終漂流到了一座無人島。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >巧合的是，同公司的三名女性同事也一同流落到這座島嶼。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你們四人必須同心協力、探索島嶼、蒐集資源，並在嚴酷的大自然中尋找生存的希望。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隨著時間流逝，在共同面對挑戰的過程中，你與她們之間的羈絆將逐漸加深，甚至可能發生意想不到的改變……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆角色介紹◆</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >太刀野 曉美</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras/5ed14010ce9771d02e82311f72ef62eb.avif?t=1761909441\" width=1280 height=720 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >曉美是你的前輩，來自業務部門。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她親切、可靠，從你入職以來一直給予你支持。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >即使你在工作上已經能獨當一面，她仍會在意你的狀況，讓你感受到安心與信賴。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras/fa145c5fe99b8b6b8f17b114221e81f2.avif?t=1761909441\" width=1280 height=720 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >星宮 夢乃</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras/92a4c0790abb68dd09dcead54b8c27d6.avif?t=1761909441\" width=1280 height=720 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的後輩同事，是一名充滿活力的年輕女性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大學時期曾是田徑部成員，體力出眾。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她對你懷有憧憬，總是積極幫助你，在荒島生活中展現出非凡的行動力。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras/2562fcc50435cdc22ed283f98f3f4a94.avif?t=1761909441\" width=1280 height=720 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >朝霧 靜葉</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras/dd7442c95b8c5410f472684392520a6f.avif?t=1761909441\" width=1280 height=720 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >來自總務部的女性員工，已婚。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她沉著冷靜，待人溫和，並且擅長照顧人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >雖然平時與你的交流不多，但在困境中，她展現出了值得依賴的一面。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras/cb5e38d6a196564045ff08f8ea3e4ac8.avif?t=1761909441\" width=1280 height=720 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆遊戲特色◆</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇攜手合作生存◇</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自由探索島嶼、蒐集食物與水源、製作工具與設施，讓生活逐漸邁向穩定。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但大自然與猛獸的威脅，也將考驗你的判斷與領導。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras/a0ad534b1acd118fdd1a372f387dc262.avif?t=1761909441\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras_big/a0ad534b1acd118fdd1a372f387dc262.webp?t=1761909441 width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇逐漸加深的羈絆◇</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與同事們的互動將隨著時間而改變。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >從依賴到信任，甚至發展出浪漫情愫，還可能伴隨矛盾與考驗...？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras/a50756bcb3d2c95a1d960780701412a3.avif?t=1761909441\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras_big/a50756bcb3d2c95a1d960780701412a3.webp?t=1761909441 width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇戀愛與成人場景◇</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隨著彼此的信任累積，你將有機會體驗更親密的互動。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是否發展成友情、愛情，甚至更多樣的關係，都取決於你的選擇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras/038724ea783208d5d7aad32cb840858f.avif?t=1761909441\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras_big/038724ea783208d5d7aad32cb840858f.webp?t=1761909441 width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇多重路線與結局◇</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >無論你是想專注於某個角色、維持微妙的平衡，還是挑戰「多人的浪漫♥」，每一個選擇都將通向不同的命運！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras/7734c9d2269aa15bc2a5158090f13296.avif?t=1761909441\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras_big/7734c9d2269aa15bc2a5158090f13296.webp?t=1761909441 width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras/797d4be35afaae580f641e3c1f5efc43.avif?t=1761909441\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras_big/797d4be35afaae580f641e3c1f5efc43.webp?t=1761909441 width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆遊戲系統◆</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇狀態與資源管理◇</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >掌握角色壓力、體力與好感度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >水與食物是關鍵資源，必須謹慎地規劃探索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >忽視管理會導致飢餓或異常狀態！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras/40f29e7c93cc1217221328365b210031.avif?t=1761909441\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras_big/40f29e7c93cc1217221328365b210031.webp?t=1761909441 width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇行動分配與技能成長◇</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每天自由分配探索、製作、料理等行動對象，想要單獨跟誰一起還是大家一起出外探索，任你選擇！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隨著經驗累積，角色將提升生存等級，解鎖更高效的工具與技能。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras/ffbb2d828f188f3b1941efdc2c3da39e.avif?t=1761909441\" width=1280 height=720 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇探索與戰鬥◇</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >雖然自然資源豐富，但猛獸與環境變化會帶來危險。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >善用製作出來的武器，謹慎思考每一步戰略，才能確保生存。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras/a6d4050e045023f6345c054193ab6b8b.avif?t=1761909441\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras_big/a6d4050e045023f6345c054193ab6b8b.webp?t=1761909441 width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇人際關係與發展◇</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >角色的壓力與心情，甚至身體狀況，都會影響到人際互動。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >透過對話交流提升好感度，解鎖專屬事件或是更進一步的發展！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras/478b39975c24c2a835759fd2be5302e6.avif?t=1761909441\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras_big/478b39975c24c2a835759fd2be5302e6.webp?t=1761909441 width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔀 最終抉擇</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了關係走向之外，你們還將面臨終極選擇：是在無人島建立新生活，還是等待救援歸來？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆內容規格◆</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・登錄於回想模式的事件數量： 44 種</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・具備「回想模式全解鎖」功能（需滿足特定條件）</p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras/d9fb2ec2a5c691a43d3a2a6853e13126.avif?t=1761909441\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆遊戲背景概要◆</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一趟員工旅遊中，你與同事們搭乘的郵輪不幸沉沒，最終漂流到了一座無人島。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >巧合的是，同公司的三名女性同事也一同流落到這座島嶼。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你們四人必須同心協力、探索島嶼、蒐集資源，並在嚴酷的大自然中尋找生存的希望。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隨著時間流逝，在共同面對挑戰的過程中，你與她們之間的羈絆將逐漸加深，甚至可能發生意想不到的改變……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆角色介紹◆</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >太刀野 曉美</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras/5ed14010ce9771d02e82311f72ef62eb.avif?t=1761909441\" width=1280 height=720 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >曉美是你的前輩，來自業務部門。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她親切、可靠，從你入職以來一直給予你支持。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >即使你在工作上已經能獨當一面，她仍會在意你的狀況，讓你感受到安心與信賴。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras/fa145c5fe99b8b6b8f17b114221e81f2.avif?t=1761909441\" width=1280 height=720 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >星宮 夢乃</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras/92a4c0790abb68dd09dcead54b8c27d6.avif?t=1761909441\" width=1280 height=720 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的後輩同事，是一名充滿活力的年輕女性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大學時期曾是田徑部成員，體力出眾。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她對你懷有憧憬，總是積極幫助你，在荒島生活中展現出非凡的行動力。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras/2562fcc50435cdc22ed283f98f3f4a94.avif?t=1761909441\" width=1280 height=720 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >朝霧 靜葉</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras/dd7442c95b8c5410f472684392520a6f.avif?t=1761909441\" width=1280 height=720 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >來自總務部的女性員工，已婚。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她沉著冷靜，待人溫和，並且擅長照顧人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >雖然平時與你的交流不多，但在困境中，她展現出了值得依賴的一面。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras/cb5e38d6a196564045ff08f8ea3e4ac8.avif?t=1761909441\" width=1280 height=720 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆遊戲特色◆</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇攜手合作生存◇</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自由探索島嶼、蒐集食物與水源、製作工具與設施，讓生活逐漸邁向穩定。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但大自然與猛獸的威脅，也將考驗你的判斷與領導。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras/a0ad534b1acd118fdd1a372f387dc262.avif?t=1761909441\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras_big/a0ad534b1acd118fdd1a372f387dc262.webp?t=1761909441 width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇逐漸加深的羈絆◇</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與同事們的互動將隨著時間而改變。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >從依賴到信任，甚至發展出浪漫情愫，還可能伴隨矛盾與考驗...？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras/a50756bcb3d2c95a1d960780701412a3.avif?t=1761909441\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras_big/a50756bcb3d2c95a1d960780701412a3.webp?t=1761909441 width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇戀愛與成人場景◇</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隨著彼此的信任累積，你將有機會體驗更親密的互動。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是否發展成友情、愛情，甚至更多樣的關係，都取決於你的選擇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras/038724ea783208d5d7aad32cb840858f.avif?t=1761909441\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras_big/038724ea783208d5d7aad32cb840858f.webp?t=1761909441 width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇多重路線與結局◇</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >無論你是想專注於某個角色、維持微妙的平衡，還是挑戰「多人的浪漫♥」，每一個選擇都將通向不同的命運！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras/7734c9d2269aa15bc2a5158090f13296.avif?t=1761909441\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras_big/7734c9d2269aa15bc2a5158090f13296.webp?t=1761909441 width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras/797d4be35afaae580f641e3c1f5efc43.avif?t=1761909441\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras_big/797d4be35afaae580f641e3c1f5efc43.webp?t=1761909441 width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆遊戲系統◆</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇狀態與資源管理◇</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >掌握角色壓力、體力與好感度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >水與食物是關鍵資源，必須謹慎地規劃探索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >忽視管理會導致飢餓或異常狀態！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras/40f29e7c93cc1217221328365b210031.avif?t=1761909441\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras_big/40f29e7c93cc1217221328365b210031.webp?t=1761909441 width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇行動分配與技能成長◇</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每天自由分配探索、製作、料理等行動對象，想要單獨跟誰一起還是大家一起出外探索，任你選擇！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隨著經驗累積，角色將提升生存等級，解鎖更高效的工具與技能。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras/ffbb2d828f188f3b1941efdc2c3da39e.avif?t=1761909441\" width=1280 height=720 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇探索與戰鬥◇</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >雖然自然資源豐富，但猛獸與環境變化會帶來危險。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >善用製作出來的武器，謹慎思考每一步戰略，才能確保生存。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras/a6d4050e045023f6345c054193ab6b8b.avif?t=1761909441\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras_big/a6d4050e045023f6345c054193ab6b8b.webp?t=1761909441 width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇人際關係與發展◇</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >角色的壓力與心情，甚至身體狀況，都會影響到人際互動。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >透過對話交流提升好感度，解鎖專屬事件或是更進一步的發展！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras/478b39975c24c2a835759fd2be5302e6.avif?t=1761909441\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/extras_big/478b39975c24c2a835759fd2be5302e6.webp?t=1761909441 width=1560 height=877 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔀 最終抉擇</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了關係走向之外，你們還將面臨終極選擇：是在無人島建立新生活，還是等待救援歸來？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆內容規格◆</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・登錄於回想模式的事件數量： 44 種</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・具備「回想模式全解鎖」功能（需滿足特定條件）</p>", "short_description": "在一趟員工旅遊中，你與同事們搭乘的郵輪不幸沉沒，最終漂流到了一座無人島。 巧合的是，同公司的三名女性同事也一同流落到這座島嶼。你們四人必須同心協力、探索島嶼、蒐集資源，並在嚴酷的大自然中尋找生存的希望。", "supported_languages": "日文<strong>*</strong>, 英文, 簡體中文, 繁體中文<br><strong>*</strong>具備完整音效支援的語言", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/86c32d54a62dbd75b9a73f337ef0f201cbae7a25/header_tchinese.jpg?t=1761909441", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/5813b4a49b003a18a8642e5bc91021e43430d03f/capsule_231x87_tchinese.jpg?t=1761909441", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2937940/5813b4a49b003a18a8642e5bc91021e43430d03f/capsule_184x69_tchinese.jpg?t=1761909441", "website": null, "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統:</strong> Windows 10<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel® Core™ 2 Duo E6600 or AMD Phenom™ X3 8750<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 8 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> HD Intel Graphics<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 12 GB 可用空間</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": [], "linux_requirements": [], "release_date": {"coming_soon": true, "date": "2027"}}}}